**Example 1: 删除日志主题**



Input: 

```
tccli cdn DeleteClsLogTopic --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --Channel cdn \
    --LogsetId 6d04373b-ba59-4a4f-a96e-9fe53b59a536 \
    --TopicId 6d04373b-ba59-4a4f-a96e-242424
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "RequestId": "6d04373b-ba59-4a4f-a96e-9fe53b59a536"
    }
}
```
